We are looking for a highly motivated and passionate senior Solution Architect to drive high priority customer initiatives on the Microsoft Azure Platform in collaboration with customers and the Microsoft field in Enterprise accounts segment of our business. This is a customer facing role, owning overall technical relationship and architectural strategy between our Professional Services customer and Microsoft. 
 
You will own technical customer engagements including architectural design, specific implementation projects to drive the customerâ€™s digital transformation. The ideal candidate will have experience in customer-facing roles and success leading deep technical architecture with senior customer executives, Enterprise Architects, IT Management and Developers to drive transformative solutions to productions. 
Responsibilities 
Requirements: 
Summary: 
You will demonstrate deep expertise in the Audit and Assurance industry and Microsoftâ€™s capability in all solution areas to help the customer drive their digital transformation. You may have a track record in our customers' industries and may have performed in positions such as CIO, CTO, CDO. The broad scope of responsibility of this role requires a solid understanding of both business and technology strategy, change management, and a principled approach to broad digital transformation challenges and opportunities. You may also share a common set of characteristics, such as strong leadership and people skills, and bring the experience that drive innovation and customer value. 
Exhibit Audit Industry CTO Principals: 
Strong executive presence, presentation, and communication skills (Required) 
