Familiarity with the entire MS technical solution stack (Azure, Modern Work, Biz Apps) - Technically depth in Azure = 200-300 level (Required) 
Understand the cloud best practice patterns (Required) and Microsoft's Cloud Adoption Framework and Well Architected Framework principles (Preferred) 
Interpret requirements, business outcomes and map to technical architecture (Required) 
Familiar with the professional services industry, the audit and assurance business and interpret the Customerâ€™s Audit CIO strategy (Preferred) 
